{"tid":2273979,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾投訴警跪頸 網媒女記者變被告","createTime":"2020-11-06T06:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T08:14:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2bcfe1cfcec7b8d127377527b13aa17d65c2ff19","tid":2273979,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/U6EZKMCTYFCQ3C7VT2I57U7OWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FU6EZKMCTYFCQ3C7VT2I57U7OWE%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8iSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=5a6835b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FU6EZKMCTYFCQ3C7VT2I57U7OWE%2F&h=2ca65fc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/U6EZKMCTYFCQ3C7VT2I57U7OWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n曾投訴警跪頸 網媒女記者變被告<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網媒「娛賓」一名女記者今年母親節晚於旺角洗衣街公園採訪期間，稱被防暴警噴椒，再遭按地用膝蓋跪頸致失去意識及失禁，當時警方曾以涉公眾地方行為不檢將她拘捕，事隔半年，重案組昨晨上門，再以涉嫌「抗拒警務人員」拘捕她，下周一提堂。有立法會議員批評，警方濫捕及顛倒是非，令警暴受害人變被告。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：傳媒工會聯手轟警恐嚇 美促停損新聞自由<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8gN8-0sJsYbDEPOosdRj6SEkxjA=/2141x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RLUYVSM6EBBO5GWIYWZWLL4TXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8gN8-0sJsYbDEPOosdRj6SEkxjA%3D%2F2141x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRLUYVSM6EBBO5GWIYWZWLL4TXY.jpg&h=24ae9482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■娛賓女記者KY今年5.10採訪期間疑於公廁內遭警暴，需由救護員送院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遭控抗拒警務人員<br />\n<br />\n今年5月10日母親節當晚，網媒娛賓女記者KY於旺角採訪，當時她報稱因生理需要，穿着黃背心及戴記者證進入洗衣街公園女廁，目擊兩名防暴警用索帶索上兩名少女的手。防暴警續衝前搶去她的相機並把她推向牆，不斷向其面部、鼻及耳朵噴射胡椒噴霧，其後四至五名警員將她按地，用膝蓋跪向其頸側、用腳踢背、用棍打頭，令她短暫失去意識。KY醒來後發現雙手被綁及失禁，曾向警員要求喝水，當時有女警竟用水向她「兜頭淋」。她送院時頭部腫脹，手背及頭部痛楚。警方當晚稱，一名26歲女子懷疑於廁所內拍照，警方警告停止拍攝遭拒，遂使用胡椒噴劑制服，該女子涉公眾地方行為不檢被捕。<br />\n<br />\n事隔半年，娛賓昨於fb發文，指該台女記者KY早上約8時被警方上門拘捕，公司已委託律師跟進事件。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：前私隱專員蔣任宏：運署忽略傳媒豁免<br />\n對再有傳媒人被捕，立法會議員尹兆堅質疑警方再拘捕曾遭警員跪頸致失知覺及失禁的女記者是濫捕及顛倒是非黑白，令警暴受害人變被告，非常離譜。他指其團隊已聯絡律師為被捕人提供協助，日後會研究是否追究警員涉濫暴責任。<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅質疑，警方近日連串針對記者的拘捕行動是政治報復，因為不滿記者近月多次藉錄像或新聞揭露警方濫權，令警方形象受損。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_8A-WjK_GrU-fmdBRSK3IXwsud8=/591x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OA6YCGFQ7ZCILPUQU4LUSMWSKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_8A-WjK_GrU-fmdBRSK3IXwsud8%3D%2F591x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOA6YCGFQ7ZCILPUQU4LUSMWSKM.jpg&h=c4770bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■女記者當日送院時被鎖上手銬。"},{"pid":"47838489e2bfe277f530533aeadcb5ce8b839b0e","tid":2273979,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:37:06.000Z","msg":"中共deep state政治真係咁黑暗"},{"pid":"b555f9734132edbcdf58ba0156b1c4928d5feffa","tid":2273979,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a529cd0cfe3dd8e2a960e7f42a90f1482bb6c1","tid":2273979,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:45:55.000Z","msg":"記者工會出聲未？"},{"pid":"66c54c8a79b21a4ad261287935823ea1b9090e29","tid":2273979,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7257ce03ea10786712386ff438f2def62d90b4","tid":2273979,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:46:40.000Z","msg":"頂"},{"